{"id":3291,"date":"2020-08-19T13:46:11","date_gmt":"2020-08-19T13:46:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/?page_id=3291"},"modified":"2020-08-25T17:08:18","modified_gmt":"2020-08-25T17:08:18","slug":"african-missions","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/african-missions\/","title":{"rendered":"African Missions"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"3291\" class=\"elementor elementor-3291\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2f842a9 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2f842a9\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-55378cb\" data-id=\"55378cb\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3ea35c8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3ea35c8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">African Missions<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5edd664\" data-id=\"5edd664\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section data-particle_enable=\"false\" data-particle-mobile-disabled=\"false\" class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-37b9807 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"37b9807\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f548933\" data-id=\"f548933\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46d4f51 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"46d4f51\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Africa Missions dates back to 1996, when Pastor (Mrs) Folu Adeboye (Visionaire of Africa Missions) went on a visit to mission fields in West Africa. She came back with a burden and the clarion call that the missions desperately needed assistance. This led to the birth of the then \u2018West Africa Missions Committee\u2019, a group which focused on assisting mission fields in the West African sub-region alone.<\/p><p>The scope of the committee was enlarged in area of reach and focus to include the rest of Africa and community development work for the host communities of the mission fields. This development came as a result of another missionary journey she embarked upon, in 1997, to the Central, Eastern and Southern parts of Africa.<\/p><p>Today, the Africa Missions Organisation is a fully fledged faith-based not- for- profit organisation committed to addressing the plight of the less privileged in Africa and around the world through appropriate community development and empowerment initiatives and the good news of the gospel of Jesus Christ.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3c9bcff\" data-id=\"3c9bcff\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2713c0b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2713c0b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-1024x1024.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-3423\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-1536x1536.png 1536w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-2048x2048.png 2048w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-400x400.png 400w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-600x600.png 600w, https:\/\/www.rccg.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/208-2089134_rccg-logo-redeemed-christian-church-logo-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t